docs.lead_paragraph: The United States Mail steamship Illinois, CHAS. T. BOGGS. U. S. N., Commander, left Aspinwall at 2:20 on the morning of Oct. 21, and arrived at Quarantine at 2:30 P. M. yesterday. She brings the California Mails of Oct. 6,393 passengers, and $1,681,967 in treasure on freight.
